'''萨福德'''（{{lang-en|Safford}}，{{le|西阿帕契語|Western Apache language}}：Ichʼįʼ Nahiłtį́į́<ref>{{citation |author=William J. de Reuse |title=A Practical Grammar of the San Carlos Apache Language |publisher=Lincom Europa |year=2006 }}</ref>）位于[[美国|美国]][[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]东南部，是[[格雷厄姆县_(亚利桑那州)|格雷厄姆县]]的县治所在{{GR|6}}，面积20.6平方公里。根据[[2000年美国人口普查|2000年美国人口普查]]，共有9,232人，其中[[白人|白人]]占75.17%、[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]]占1.41%、[[土著美国人|土著美国人]]占1.01%。{{GR|2}}這個數字於2010年上升至9,566人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/ |title=2010 census factfinder2 |accessdate=2013-08-01 |archive-date=2013-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911234518/http://factfinder2.census.gov/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=popest2>{{cite web|date=2010-04-01 |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_DP_DPDP1&prodType=table |title=Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics: 2010 |format=[[Comma-separated_values|CSV]] |work=2010 Demographic Profile Data |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau, Population Division |accessdate=2010-04-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305164937/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_DP_DPDP1&prodType=table |archivedate=2014-03-05}}</ref>

==地理==
萨福德的座標為{{coord|32|49|24|N|109|42|53|W|type:city}}（32.823266,-109.714613）。{{GR|1}}根據[[美國2000年人口普查|2000年人口普查]]，本城面積為{{convert|8.6|sqmi|sqkm|2}}，其中{{convert|8.6|sqmi|sqkm|2}}為陸地，{{convert|0.03|sqmi|sqkm|2}}為水域。<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2013-01-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

